thread.title_full: PAS Youth meets archbishop at KL church

title: PAS Youth meets archbishop at KL church

persons.name: nik mohamad abduh nik abdul aziz

text:
More 
PAS Youth yesterday visited St Anthony Church at Jalan Pudu, Kuala Lumpur to have a dialogue on racial and religious harmony. 
The delegation led by PAS Youth chief Nik Mohamad Abduh Nik Abdul Aziz was received by Archbishop Julian Leow. 
"PAS Youth used this opportunity to explain about the Budaya Politik Matang Sejahtera (Harmonious and Mature Political Culture) implemented by PAS today," PAS Youth assistant secretary Nurul Islam Mohamad Yusoff said.
